data.name: pyAscoreValidation
data.description: Validation experiments for the pyAscore python package.

evidence: "Here you can find the pipeline and notebooks of results from our validation experiments for the pyAscore python package. All experiments were performed with Snakemake, and the pipeline should reproduce all search and scoring results from our manuscript."

"Original results and figures which were included in the manuscript are available in the following notebook files. These can be directly viewed in Github or downloaded and re-run with the re-created analysis on your own machine."
The repository owner is a single GitHub user (owner_login: AnthonyOfSeattle), with no mention of an institution, lab, or community project in the README.
